# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
# BOTTOM BAR â€” mini-player only (shown during play/pause; hidden when stopped)
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

# â”€â”€ Mini-player bar background (playing/paused: 50px with art, title, indicator) â”€â”€
# Keep this in the normal SBS plane. `%VB` here would turn the pill into the
# active LCD backdrop, and list/menu clears would replay stale boot/WPS pixels.
%V(0,190,320,50,-)
%?if(%cs, =, 10)<|%?mp<|%xd(Z)||%xd(Z)|%xd(Z)>>

# â”€â”€ Mini-player content (playing state â€” 50px container) â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€

# Album art in mini-player (32x32, vertically centered in the rounded rectangle)
# Draw the corner mask after %Cd in this same viewport so the small art path
# cannot drift out of sync with the live album bitmap.
%V(16,197,32,32,-)
%Cl(0,0,32,32)
%?if(%cs, =, 10)<|%?mp<|%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<%Cd%xd(Y)|>>||%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<%Cd%xd(Y)|>>|%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<%Cd%xd(Y)|>>>>

# Track title in mini-player (font slot 8, RB12 h=18; compact tier for bar fit)
%V(60,204,214,18,8)
%Vf(000000)
%?if(%cs, =, 10)<|%?mp<|%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<%s%al%?it<%it|%fn>|>>||%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<%s%al%?it<%it|%fn>|>>|%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<%s%al%?it<%it|%fn>|>>>>

# Track title shifted left when no album art
%V(24,204,250,18,8)
%Vf(000000)
%?if(%cs, =, 10)<|%?mp<|%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<|%s%al%?it<%it|%fn>>>||%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<|%s%al%?it<%it|%fn>>>|%?mv(1.2)<|%?C<|%s%al%?it<%it|%fn>>>>>

# Play/pause indicator in mini-player â€” 16x18 Apple-native icon, right-aligned
# Pa=stop  Pb=pause-bars  Pc=play-triangle  Pd=ff
# Branch: 0=stop(hidden) 1=playâ†’Pc(play-fill) 2=pauseâ†’Pb(pause-bars) 3+=Pc
%V(280,203,20,20,-)
%?if(%cs, =, 10)<|%?mp<|%?mv(1.2)<|%xd(Tc)>|%?mv(1.2)<|%xd(Tb)>|%?mv(1.2)<|%xd(Tc)>|%?mv(1.2)<|%xd(Tc)>>>

# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
# VOLUME BARS â€” rendered inside the 50px mini-player bar when adjusting volume
# Positioned to match WPS volume bar: 20px viewport, bar at y=8 within viewport
# giving the same absolute visual center as the WPS volume bar.
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
# Small volume bar
%Vl(mp_volume_bg,60,203,196,20,-)
%Vf(6E6E73)
%Vb(FFFFFF)
%?if(%pv, >, 0)<|%pv(0,8,-,4,noborder)>

# Small volume bar (clipping â€” red)
%Vl(mp_volume_clip,60,203,196,20,-)
%Vf(FF2D55)
