# QUICK SETTINGS â€” Apple2026 custom overlay
# Themeify-inspired composition:
# - smaller grey wheel centered in the surface
# - brightness as the primary focus above / below the wheel
# - thin WPS-like horizontal utility bars underneath
# Core still owns the runtime map and suppresses the native quickscreen body.
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

